The official launch of Rihanna’s Fenty Beauty and Skin took place in Johannesburg at the Monarch restaurant in Sandton on Thursday evening. Hector Espinal, who is the the brand’s global makeup artist was the special guest of the night. The who’s who of the industry all flocked to the much-anticipated event, which everyone was looking forward to. Although there was no specific theme or dress code there were some stunning looks that stole the show. See pics here: <img class="alignnone wp-image-190241 size-full" src="https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Rosemary-Candice-scaled.jpg" alt="" width="1078" height="1920" srcset="https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Rosemary-Candice-scaled.jpg 719w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Rosemary-Candice-140x250.jpg 140w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Rosemary-Candice-449x800.jpg 449w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Rosemary-Candice-768x1368.jpg 768w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Rosemary-Candice-863x1536.jpg 863w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Rosemary-Candice-696x1239.jpg 696w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Rosemary-Candice-1068x1902.jpg 1068w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Rosemary-Candice-236x420.jpg 236w" sizes="(max-width: 1078px) 100vw, 1078px" />    For the latest entertainment news from Sunday World, click here. Or read the latest from Shwashwi here. Follow @SundayWorldZA on Twitter and @sundayworldza on Instagram, or like our Facebook Page, Sunday World, by clicking here for the latest breaking news in South Africa. To Subscribe to Sunday World, click here.